listings.comment: Collaborating with Harun on a website development project left room for improvement. The project didn't go as far as we wanted, but Harun tried as hard as we could to make it happen. Additionally, working with him was challenging due to language barriers.

I mean this wholeheartedly—these are the best people I’ve worked with on Fiverr. They know what they’re doing and consistently deliver top-quality results. I highly recommend anyone looking to get a website to go with Harun Miah—you won’t be disappointed. In fact, they should be Pro Level on Fiverr instead of Level 2—that’s how good they are!

Working with Harun Miah in website development was a generally positive experience, although there were some challenges along the way. Improvements in attention to detail and communication skills, especially in language fluency, could enhance the overall collaborative process. Despite these hurdles, Harun was incredibly accommodating throughout the revisions, ultimately delivering a final product that matched my vision.

He was willing to do a zoom call with me to discuss my revisions live and helped me along the way. I didn't know the first thing about word press and now I can use it well enough to get by. Thank you Harun, I recommend him for any website projects you may have.

Harun Miah did a great job on developing our website, resulting in an impressive final product. However, focusing more on attention to detail and enhancing proactiveness could improve future projects. Overall, the cooperation was positive, though ironing out bugs took some extra time and communication could be better.

I am very happy for hiring this guy to make my website. He is very responsive to messages, built a nice website and is a hard worker! Whenever he made a major change he would create a video explaining what he did.
